---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - AgentDoor">

  <Nav currentPage="privacy" />

  <div class="section" style="padding-top: 140px; padding-bottom: 80px;">
    <div class="container-narrow" style="max-width: 720px;">
      <a href="/" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; color: var(--color-ink-tertiary); text-decoration: none; margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 0.9375rem;">
        <svg style="width: 1rem; height: 1rem;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path>
        </svg>
        Back to Home
      </a>

      <h1 style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.15; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p style="color: var(--color-ink-tertiary); margin-bottom: 3rem;">Effective Date: April 1, 2026</p>

      <div style="color: var(--color-ink-secondary); line-height: 1.8; font-size: 1.0625rem;">
        <p>AgentDoor is a project of <strong style="color: var(--color-ink);">Managed Ventures LLC</strong>, a California limited liability company.</p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-ink); margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">What We Collect</h2>
        <p>Nothing. This site does not use cookies, tracking pixels, analytics services, or contact forms. We do not create user accounts. We do not collect personal information when you browse this site.</p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-ink); margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">What We Don't Do</h2>
        <ul style="list-style: disc; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem;">
          <li>We do not collect personal data.</li>
          <li>We do not track you.</li>
          <li>We do not use cookies.</li>
          <li>We do not sell data.</li>
          <li>We do not use data to train AI models.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-ink); margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Downloads and Open Source Software</h2>
        <p>Software available for download on this site (Geniuz, Token Scout, Sendblue MCP) is open source under the MIT License. Downloading software does not require providing personal information. We do not collect telemetry or usage data from installed software.</p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-ink); margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of any personal information we hold about you by emailing <a href="mailto:legal@managedv.com" style="color: var(--color-accent); text-decoration: underline;">legal@managedv.com</a>. California residents have additional rights under the CCPA, including the right to know what information we have collected and the right to request deletion. We do not sell personal information.</p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-ink); margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Security</h2>
        <p>We use standard security practices to protect any information you provide. However, no method of transmission over the internet is completely secure.</p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-ink); margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Changes</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be reflected in the effective date above.</p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-ink); margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Managed Ventures LLC<br/>
          Email: <a href="mailto:legal@managedv.com" style="color: var(--color-accent); text-decoration: underline;">legal@managedv.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <Footer />

</Layout>
